title: The Mission
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Fast food, Mexican, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Mexican burrito place that offers some vegan options. Try the vegetarian burrito without the sour cream and cheese. The guacamole and all salsas are vegan. Any questions, ask for their ingredients' list. Has children's menu. A second location can be found in Oxford on King Edward St.
